## Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ExpertDecisionReplayPlatform.git
```

### Create Virtual Environment

```bash
python -m venv venv
```

### Activate

Windows

```bash
venv\Scripts\activate
```

Linux

```bash
source venv/bin/activate
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Run Backend

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

### Run Frontend

```bash
npm install
npm start
```

